message: Rebecca Bender Initiative is doing amazing work helping survivors heal and thrive!! Learn more about Elevate program and how it is impacting survivors nationwide! http://www.rebeccabender.org/elevate/

data.description: Rebecca Bender is a survivor of human trafficking. Rebecca Bender Initiative is based in Oregon but serves victims of sex trafficking worldwide. RBI also equips first responders in identifying victims.
data.title: Elevate Academy
